</div></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class="col-lg-5"> </div></div></div></div></div><div class="panel panel-default"><div class="panel-heading"><h4 id="Slot1-2" class="panel-title"><span style="float: right;">Resource Conformance: supported </span>Slot</h4></div><div class="panel-body"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-lg-6"><span class="lead">Base System Profile</span><br/><a href="StructureDefinition-sas-sos-slot-aggregator.html">FrSlotAgregateurSOS</a></div><div class="col-lg-3"><span class="lead">Conformité au Profil</span><br/><b>SHALL</b></div><div class="col-lg-3"><span class="lead">Reference Policy</span><br/></div></div><p/><div class="row"><div class="col-lg-6"><span class="lead">Résumé des interactions</span><br/><ul><li>Supports <code>read</code>, <code>search-type</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><div class="row"><div class="col-lg-7"><span class="lead">Paramètres de recherche</span><table class="table table-condensed table-hover"><thead><tr><th>Conformité</th><th>Paramètre</th><th>Type</th><th>Documentation</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href="SearchParameter-slot-sp-start.html">SPDateDebutSlot</a></td><td><code>date</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche d'une disponibilité sur la date et l'heure de début de disponibilité souhaité</p>
</div></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class="col-lg-5"> </div></div></div></div></div><div class="panel panel-default"><div class="panel-heading"><h4 id="Location1-3" class="panel-title"><span style="float: right;">Resource Conformance: supported </span>Location</h4></div><div class="panel-body"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-lg-6"><span class="lead">Base System Profile</span><br/><a href="StructureDefinition-sas-sos-location-aggregator.html">FrLocationAgregateurSOS</a></div><div class="col-lg-3"><span class="lead">Conformité au Profil</span><br/><b>SHALL</b></div><div class="col-lg-3"><span class="lead">Reference Policy</span><br/></div></div><p/><div class="row"><div class="col-lg-6"><span class="lead">Résumé des interactions</span><br/><ul><li>Supports <code>read</code>, <code>search-type</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><div class="row"><div class="col-lg-7"><span class="lead">Paramètres de recherche</span><table class="table table-condensed table-hover"><thead><tr><th>Conformité</th><th>Paramètre</th><th>Type</th><th>Documentation</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/location.html#search">Location-organization</a></td><td><code>reference</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche d'un lieu selon la structure rattachée</p>
</div></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class="col-lg-5"> </div></div></div></div></div><div class="panel panel-default"><div class="panel-heading"><h4 id="Organization1-4" class="panel-title"><span style="float: right;">Resource Conformance: supported </span>Organization</h4></div><div class="panel-body"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-lg-6"><span class="lead">Base System Profile</span><br/><a href="StructureDefinition-sas-sos-organization-aggregator.html">FrOrganizationAgregateurSOS</a></div><div class="col-lg-3"><span class="lead">Conformité au Profil</span><br/><b>SHALL</b></div><div class="col-lg-3"><span class="lead">Reference Policy</span><br/></div></div><p/><div class="row"><div class="col-lg-6"><span class="lead">Résumé des interactions</span><br/><ul><li>Supports <code>read</code>, <code>search-type</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><div class="row"><div class="col-lg-7"><span class="lead">Paramètres de recherche</span><table class="table table-condensed table-hover"><thead><tr><th>Conformité</th><th>Paramètre</th><th>Type</th><th>Documentation</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/organization.html#search">Organization-identifier</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche d'une structure par identifiant - SIRET dans ce cas</p>
